"title": "5933: restlessness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5933",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A lack of peace, experienced physically, spiritually or mentally.</p>\n<h2>Causes of restlessness</h2>\n<h3>Worry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:12\">ECC 5:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:23\">JER 49:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:8\">GEN 41:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:1\">EST 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:16\">PRO 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:1\">DAN 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:18-Dan6:19\">DAN 6:18–6:19</a></p>\n<h3>Illness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:4-Job7:5\">JOB 7:4–7:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:2-Ps6:6\">PSA 6:2–6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3-Ps32:4\">PSA 32:3–32:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:3-Ps38:10\">PSA 38:3–38:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:13-Isa38:14\">ISA 38:13–38:14</a></p>\n<h3>Lack of purpose</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:22-Eccl2:23\">ECC 2:22–2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:4-Ps107:5\">PSA 107:4–107:5</a></p>\n<h3>Uncompleted business</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:18\">RUT 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Rebelliousness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:40\">GEN 27:40</a></p>\n<h3>Demon-possession</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:3-Mark5:5\">MRK 5:3–5:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:29\">LUK 8:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:43\">MAT 12:43</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:24\">LUK 11:24</a></p>\n<h3>Sinfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:20-Isa57:21\">ISA 57:20–57:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:13\">JUD 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:17\">JOB 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:15\">PSA 59:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:22\">ISA 48:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:10\">JER 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:6\">JER 50:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:20-1Tim6:21\">1TI 6:20–6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:8\">JAS 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:11\">REV 14:11</a></p>\n<h2>Restlessness as part of God's judgment against sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:65-Deut28:67\">DEU 28:65–28:67</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:11-Gen4:14\">GEN 4:11–4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:40\">PSA 107:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:10\">PSA 109:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:15\">LAM 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:12\">AMO 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:2\">ZEC 10:2</a></p>\n<h2>Antidotes to restlessness</h2>\n<h3>Trusting in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:1\">PSA 62:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3\">ISA 26:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:15\">ISA 30:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6\">PHP 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:14\">EXO 33:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:10\">PSA 46:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:17\">ISA 32:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:16\">JER 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31-Matt6:32\">MAT 6:31–6:32</a></p>\n<h3>Trusting in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:30\">MAT 11:28–11:30</a></strong></p>",
